description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if the Ethereum Name Service governance token, $ENS, is listed for trading on Coinbase on or before the resolution time, November 18th 2021, 11:59 PM ET. 

Specifically, if Coinbase allows users from at least one country to buy or sell $ENS before the resolution date, this market will resolve to "Yes." Otherwise, it will resolve to "No".

The resolution source for this market is the Coinbase (https://www.coinbase.com/) trading platform. 

Please note, if after this market's inception and before the resolution date Coinbase list $ENS and it is available to trade, but for any reason stops it and is not be allowed to be traded thereafter, this market will still resolve to "Yes."

Please note if $ENS will be available to trade only for Coinbase Pro users, it will not be sufficient to resolve this market to "Yes," it must be available on the main version of the site. In addition, Coinbase Wallet will not be sufficient to resolve this market to "Yes."
